{"tid":1096971,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"另一半嘅相處方式","createTime":"2019-04-08T05:43:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T12:27:03.000Z","uid":202589,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7a4a181ca59d30e327664ab22cd10669a8f19f66","tid":1096971,"uid":202589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T05:43:38.000Z","msg":"拍左兩年 最近散左  <br />\n諗返後期 日日Facetime  變到好安逸 <br />\n產生左個好危險嘅諗法 以為咁嘅日子係穩定嘅象徵<br />\n各自返屋企就打俾對方 <br />\n<br />\n但係其實又夠唔夠空間比雙方？<br />\n<br />\n究竟拍耐咗 相處方式應該係點<br />\n之前我認為 一空閒就打比女朋友係正常不過嘅事<br />\n我以為佢都係咁諗  即使各自各做嘢但有對方陪住<br />\n<br />\n漸漸覺得今日傾少啲 聽日都仲有機會傾<br />\n<br />\n邊個會估到嗰次係最後一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa6884adc9d9253f9296c202f2cca89fdaab5067","tid":1096971,"uid":188297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T05:45:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"23163c57dfba035c965c36947afd636b5551b72d","tid":1096971,"uid":202589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa6884adc9d9253f9296c202f2cca89fdaab5067","tid":1096971,"uid":188297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T05:45:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T05:50:32.000Z","msg":"日日facetime 真係好事？ <br />\n會唔會想有返小小私人空間 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55eb8754b2923d4a7ce8124754b88d184d7e79d","tid":1096971,"uid":237084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T05:52:06.000Z","msg":"即係點？<br />\n後期係比前期傾多咗定少咗？"},{"pid":"e98e4f495234956dfc7da220cdddb9ac6731dd7f","tid":1096971,"uid":177288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T05:55:36.000Z","msg":"我完全唔明<br />\n<br />\n樓主要日日facetime條女嫌你煩?"},{"pid":"e012e552ed50299d615ebb8c21a5043c2d1f7aeb","tid":1096971,"uid":202589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e55eb8754b2923d4a7ce8124754b88d184d7e79d","tid":1096971,"uid":237084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"